ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38522eef649140d9fd087a0dc47bb5c6e82906f0","tid":184113,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港食野等於幫人交租</blockquote><br />\n係香港生存等於送錢比地產商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce24367c569c7dc1c68ae6f75def69dbb2460b0","tid":184113,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431dd1af579c9c997c00590d3849816741bb9875","tid":184113,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"點解重未有人屌鳩芒果佬"},{"pid":"c43be8e4b43486a67557e106f1e99df5d24a13d6","tid":184113,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>向香港，只要你有錢 乜野高級野都食到<br />\n但向台北就未必得</blockquote><br />\n香港人多數都垃圾窮撚<br />\n所以成日會著眼於街邊流動小食<br />\n（但其實好撚污糟，以前地溝油果D，最初爆出黎源頭使用正是台灣小食鋪）<br />\n<br />\n通常去得旅行，窮撚極都唔會折墜到去食街邊野當正餐<br />\n梗係正正經經入餐廳坐，比起餐廳種類／數目<br />\n<br />\n台北真係食撚得屎</blockquote><br />\n香港人最鐘意唔食正餐走去掃街喎"},{"pid":"ae38c078d7ed9cee64575f03e5c075f5716dd747","tid":184113,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89d6a3c8f858b08a08d5392372a749b6d75491b5","tid":184113,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港食野等於幫人交租</blockquote><br />\n餓撚死佢唔好食啊笨"}]}